latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY Homemade Hair Mask By @amarsachdeva
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys...Are you worried about your hair?? Are they dry??? Frizzy??? Dull??? We have a perfect solution for your hair. 
Today, @amarsachdeva are going to share with you the homemade "Aloe Vera Hair Mask" that makes your hair silky, smooth & shiny.

Procedure:- 1) Mix Fresh or Packaged Aloe vera gel + Virgin Coconut oil in 1:2 ratio
2) Apply on your hairs
3) Leave it for half an hour
4) Wash with shampoo 
Benefits:- 1) Reduce inflammation
2) Reduce scalp irritation
3) It gives nourishment & strengthens the hairs
4) Provides Silky, Smooth & shiny hairs
5) Naturally, stimulate hair growth
6) Restores the pH balance of your hair according to your hair needs .
